column5: I volunteer at a Gymnastics club, we are trying to get this great athlete Athlete of the month award.  If you guys could vote as much as you can and help this girl out it would be greatly appreciated.  Here is the link and her name is Lee-Ann Skulj-Thompson, vote as many time as you can.  The poll is a quarter down in the middle of the page.  http://www.wellandtribune.ca/  Thanks  Charlie
1 vote per member in my household, done!= 4 votes.
